The paper discusses the use of memristor networks for intelligent data analysis applications, which falls under the category of cs.ET (Emerging Technologies). The paper also mentions the use of memristors in circuits for increased intelligence, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.AR (Hardware Architecture). The focus on solving logic puzzles using memristive circuits suggests a connection to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
